@startuml
' PlantUML Diagram for RTP Notice Status API
' Title: RTP Notice Status Sequence Diagram
' Version: 1.0.0
' Description: GET /noticeNumber/{payeeId}
'              Returns delivery status + RTP processing date (send date)

!theme materia

title RTP Notice Status API: GET /noticeNumber/{payeeId}

actor "**Service Provider**" as SP
participant "**rtp-sender**" as RS
database "**Database**" as DB

autonumber "<b>[0]"

SP -> RS: **GET** /noticeNumber/{payeeId}
activate RS

note right of RS
  **Operation:** `getNoticeStatus`
  The SP queries delivery status for a noticeNumber
  filtered by payeeId.
end note

RS -> RS: Validate Security Token

alt #palegreen **Success case: RTP delivered**

    RS -> DB: findRtpByNoticeNumber(noticeNumber)
    activate DB
    DB --> RS: results (0..n)
    deactivate DB

    RS -> RS: Filter results by payeeId
    RS -> RS: Evaluate status (SENT)

    RS --> SP: **200 OK**\nResponse: "RTP delivered"\nprocessingDate: {savingDateTime}
    deactivate RS

else #lightyellow **Fail case: RTP not delivered**

    RS -> DB: findRtpByNoticeNumber(noticeNumber)
    activate DB
    DB --> RS: empty OR status ERROR_SEND
    deactivate DB

    note right of RS
      Treat as RTP not delivered:
      - noticeNumber not found
      - status ERROR_SEND
    end note

    RS --> SP: **404 Not Found**\nResponse: "RTP not delivered"
    deactivate RS

else #darkred **Other Errors**

    group Client-Side Errors
        RS --> SP: **400 Bad Request**\n(e.g., Invalid fiscal code, missing fields)
        RS --> SP: **401 Unauthorized**\n(e.g., Invalid or expired security token)
        RS --> SP: **403 Forbidden**\n(e.g., Insufficient permissions)
        RS --> SP: **429 Too Many Requests**\n(e.g., Rate limit exceeded)
    end group

    group Server-Side Error
         note over RS: e.g., Database connection failure, unhandled exception.
         RS -> RS: An unexpected internal error occurs
         RS --> SP: **500 Internal Server Error**
    end group

    deactivate RS

end

@enduml
